description: JavaScript bindings for the repl.it protocol
name: @replit/protocol

scripts.prepublishOnly: pbjs --force-number --force-message -t static-module -w default -o index.js ../api.proto ../client.proto && ./tools/jsdoc.js < index.js > .index.js && mv .index.js index.js && pbts -o index.d.ts index.js && sed -i.bak 's/constructor(/private constructor(/' index.d.ts && rm -f index.d.ts.bak && flowgen --interface-records --no-inexact --add-flow-header --output-file index.js.flow index.d.ts && sed -i.bak 's/declare var api: typeof npm\$namespace\$api;/export var api = npm$namespace$api;/' index.js.flow && rm -f index.js.flow.bak
